ss=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-[var(--color-primary)] bg-[var(--color-primary)]/5\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/help\">Get Help</a></nav><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><a class=\"text-xs text-white bg-[var(--color-primary)] px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md hover:bg-[var(--color-primary-light)] transition-colors\" href=\"/login\">Sign In</a></div></div><main class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto pb-16 lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><section class=\"bg-gray-50 py-16 px-4 border-b border-gray-200\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-[var(--color-primary)] uppercase tracking-wider\">Contact</span><h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-2 mb-3\">Get in Touch</h1><p class=\"text-gray-500 max-w-lg mx-auto\">Have questions about a property, partnership opportunities, or need support? We are here to help.</p></div></section><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10\"><div><div><h2 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1\">Send us a Message</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6\">Fill in the form and we will respond promptly.</p><form class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\">Full Name</label><input required=\"\" class=\"w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-2.5 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[var(--color-primary)]/20 focus:border-[var(--color-primary)]\" placeholder=\"Your name\"/></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\">Email</label><input type=\"email\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-2.5 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[var(--color-primary)]/20 focus:border-[var(--color-primary)]\" placeholder=\"you@example.com\"/></div></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\">Phone</label><input class=\"w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-2.5 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[var(--color-primary)]/20 focus:border-[var(--color-primary)]\" placeholder=\"+234 800 000 0000\"/></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\">Subject</label><select class=\"w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-2.5 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[var(--color-primary)]/20 focus:border-[var(--color-primary)]\"><option>General Inquiry</option><option>Property Question</option><option>Partnership</option><option>Become an Agent</option><option>Support</option><option>Other</option></select></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\">Message</label><textarea rows=\"4\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-2.5 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[var(--color-primary)]/20 focus:border-[var(--color-primary)] resize-none\" placeholder=\"How can we help you?\"></textarea></div><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center font-medium rounded-lg transition-all duration-150 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed px-5 py-2.5 text-sm gap-2 bg-[var(--color-primary)] text-white hover:bg-[var(--color-primary-light)] focus:ring-[var(--color-primary)] w-full\" type=\"submit\">Send Message</button></form></div></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4\">Contact Information</h3><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-primary)]/5 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><span class=\"text-base\">📍</span></div><div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">Office Address</p><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-gray-900\">No. 15 Bompai Road, Kano Municipal, Kano State</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-primary)]/5 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><span class=\"text-base\">📞</span></div><div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">Phone</p><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-gray-900\">+234 800 000 0000</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-primary)]/5 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><span class=\"text-base\">✉️</span></div><div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">Email</p><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-gray-900\">hello@mbpp.ng</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-primary)]/5 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><span class=\"text-base\">🕐</span></div><div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">Working Hours</p><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-gray-900\">Monday – Saturday, 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"text-center text-gray-400\"><svg class=\"w-8 h-8 mx-auto mb-2 opacity-50\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z\"></path><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-xs\">Map loading — Google Maps integration</p><p class=\"text-[10px] text-gray-300 mt-1\">No. 15 Bompai Road, Kano</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-[var(--color-primary)]/5 rounded-lg p-6 border border-[var(--color-primary)]/10\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Want to become an agent?</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mb-4\">We are looking for motivated agents in Kano Municipal, Fagge, Tarauni, and Nassarawa. Earn commissions on every deal you close.</p><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center font-medium rounded-lg transition-all duration-150 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed px-3.5 py-2 text-xs gap-1.5 border border-[var(--color-primary)] text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--color-primary)]/5 focus:ring-[var(--color-primary)] \">Apply as Agent</button></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-16\"><div class=\"text-center mb-8\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-[var(--color-primary)] uppercase tracking-wider\">FAQ</span><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-1\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2></div><div class=\"max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-2\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden\"><button class=\"flex items-center justify-between w-full px-5 py-4 text-left\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium text-gray-900\">How do I schedule a property viewing?</span><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 transition-transform shrink-0 \" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden\"><button class=\"flex items-center justify-between w-full px-5 py-4 text-left\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium text-gray-900\">What is a holding deposit?</span><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 transition-transform shrink-0 \" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden\"><button class=\"flex items-center justify-between w-full px-5 py-4